data.description: Step through the inviting front door of 8093 Cheri Drive, and you're greeted by a grand entrance that sets the stage for the exquisite features within. A beautifully crafted staircase beckons you upstairs, while the elegant family room with its captivating fireplace draws you further into the heart of this exceptional home.  Continue your journey through the formal dining room, passing an elegant butler's pantry that adds a touch of sophistication to your gatherings. Enter the spacious kitchen, a culinary haven equipped with a double oven, granite countertops, and a charming built-in window seat in the dining area. The seamless flow from the kitchen into the living room creates a harmonious space for both entertaining and everyday living.  The living room, a true highlight of the home, boasts a striking brick fireplace and wood beams on the ceiling, providing a cozy yet sophisticated atmosphere. From here, seamlessly transition into the sunroom, a bright and inviting space where you can unwind while enjoying the beauty of the surrounding nature.  Venture upstairs to discover two beautifully appointed bedrooms, each offering comfort and style. The master bedroom is a sanctuary in itself, featuring a fireplace that adds warmth and elegance to the space. The master bathroom is a true indulgence, with its expansive layout, wet bar, and cooler for added convenience.  As you step outside, the wooded and private lot creates a serene backdrop, offering a perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life. Combine this with the home's location in one of the most sought-after school districts in the state, and 8093 Cheri Drive becomes more than just a residence – it's a complete lifestyle package.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your own. Experience the seamless blend of elegance, functionality, and comfort that defines every inch of 8093 Cheri Drive. Welcome home.  Updates: Septic-2021 Microwave-2022 Garbage Disposal-2022 Washer/Dryer-2022
